<%- include('../partials/header', { title: 'Rio: The Soft Landing' }) %>

<main>
  <!-- Journey Hero -->
  <section class="journey-hero section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="journey-hero-label">4 days</p>
      <h1>Rio: The Soft Landing</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A grounded introduction to Brazil</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Opening -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <p class="journey-opening">Rio is a city you feel before you understand.</p>
        <p>It draws you in, but it can also feel uncertain at first.</p>
        <p>This experience is designed to remove that tension.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What This Is -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>What This Is</h2>
        <p>This is not a tour. It's a way of arriving properly.</p>
        <p>I guide you into the rhythm of the city, so you don't just visit it — you start to feel comfortable in it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I Take Care Of / What You Experience -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-two-col">
        <div>
          <h2>What I Take Care Of</h2>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>Airport arrival and orientation</li>
            <li>Safe, well-positioned accommodation</li>
            <li>A clear, relaxed structure for your days</li>
            <li>Movement through the city with awareness and ease</li>
            <li>Access to places that feel real, not touristic</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>What You Experience</h2>
          <ul class="journey-list">
            <li>The beach, without overwhelm</li>
            <li>Neighbourhoods that feel lived in</li>
            <li>Food and places chosen with intention</li>
            <li>A pace that allows you to settle, not rush</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Difference -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>The Difference</h2>
        <p>Most people pass through Rio.</p>
        <p>I help you understand how to be in it — so it becomes familiar, not intimidating.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who This Is For -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>Who This Is For</h2>
        <ul class="journey-list">
          <li>First time in Brazil</li>
          <li>Solo travellers who want support</li>
          <li>Women who want to feel safe without feeling restricted</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Changes -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="journey-content">
        <h2>What Changes</h2>
        <p>You relax.<br>You understand the rhythm.<br>You move with more confidence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="included-section">
        <div class="included-list">
          <h3>Your Investment Covers</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>4 nights of carefully selected accommodation</li>
            <li>Meals throughout your stay</li>
            <li>Internal transportation within Rio</li>
            <li>All planned experiences and activities</li>
            <li>My guidance throughout the journey</li>
            <li>Local connections and introductions</li>
            <li>Translation and cultural navigation</li>
            <li>Pre-trip planning and customisation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="included-list">
          <h3>Not Included</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>International flights to/from Brazil</li>
            <li>Travel insurance (required)</li>
            <li>Personal shopping and souvenirs</li>
            <li>Visa fees if applicable</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--color-warm-gray); font-size: 0.95rem;">I'm happy to advise on flight options and help with any logistics. Just ask.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>How We Begin</h2>
        <p>We start with a conversation. From there, I shape the experience around you.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Start the Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
